    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Broker作为起始节点。idle之后通过SCAN事件到scanned，这个scanned状态可以重复扫描吗？还有从scanned到viewing的触发条件是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "scanned",
        "SCAN"
