      "utterance": "已绘制完成。确认一下结构：Broker指向idle；idle经SCAN到scanned；scanned可自循环SCAN，也可经SELECT到viewing；viewing经BACK回scanned；两状态都有SELECT自循环和EXPORT；scanned经RESET回idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
